reqBody.prompt: Highly detailed anime-style image of an adventurer with practical attire, sturdy boots, short hair, and bright eyes. This adventurer wears simple armor with subtle designs, suitable for exploring a fantastical world. They carry a weapon, such as a magical staff, a sword (one-handed or two-handed), a bow and arrow, a pair of daggers, a katana, a spear, an axe, a mace, a war hammer, a whip, or gauntlets, and stand with their feet together, legs shoulder-width apart, and arms held straight out to the sides, ready for battle. Confident expression. Orthographic model front projection, limited color palette, deep black background.
